&nbsp;
The elder, originally from Reggio Calabria, was on board a car in the company of a 54-year-old, when it was flanked by a red Fiat 500 from which some shots of fire would start. Seriously wounded, the 81-year-old had been brought to the Umberto I Polyclinic but died the next day. On the site of the attack the scientific police recovered 5 casings. The investigations are focused on the hypothesis of a shooting between sinti and a shot that only by mistake reached the woman.&nbsp; The 28-year-old had been subjected to the arrest yesterday but obviously the elements at his expense were not considered entirely univocal.
